llowing existing patterns in [file]\"\n- \"Without adding new dependencies\"\n```\n\n#### Configure Agent/Subagent (if applicable)\n```yaml\ndescription: [Improved description with triggers]\ntools: [Restricted tool list]\n```\n\n### 📚 Lessons Learned\n**Pattern**: [What to watch for]\n**Principle**: [Underlying concept]\n**Prevention**: [Proactive measure]\n\n### ✅ Verification Steps\n1. Test the same task with new configuration\n2. Check if agent follows the new rules\n3. Iterate if needed\n\n## Analysis Guidelines\n- Be specific - reference exact files and line numbers when possible\n- Focus on prevention - rules that stop issues before they occur\n- Test recommendations - ensure they're practical and effective\n- Reference Claude Code docs - link to relevant documentation sections"
